---
title: Spiced Lamb & Caribbean Coconut Sauce with Roast Veggie Toss
description: There’s nothing better than lamb rump that’s juicy on the inside and wonderfully roasted with mild spices on the outside. That’s
how we’re preparing our protein tonight, plus add a drizzle of creamy Caribbean coconut sauce to double down on all that flavour. Delish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-lamb-coconut-sauce-da65310c.jpg
